  "Unique identifier for the subgraph deployment."
  id: ID!

  deniedAt: Int!

  originalName: String
  "Total tokens staked on the subgraph deployment."
  stakedTokens: BigInt!
  "List of indexer allocations derived from the subgraph deployment."
  indexerAllocations: [Allocation!]! @derivedFrom(field: "subgraphDeployment")
  "Total amount of indexing rewards."
  indexingRewardAmount: BigInt!
  "Amount of indexing rewards allocated to indexers."
  indexingIndexerRewardAmount: BigInt!
  "Amount of indexing rewards allocated to delegators."
  indexingDelegatorRewardAmount: BigInt!
  "Total amount of query fees collected."
  queryFeesAmount: BigInt!
  "Amount of query fee rebates."
  queryFeeRebates: BigInt!
  "Total curator fee rewards."
  curatorFeeRewards: BigInt!
  "Total tokens signalled on the subgraph deployment."
  signalledTokens: BigInt!
  "Total tokens unsignalled from the subgraph deployment."
  unsignalledTokens: BigInt!
  "Current signal amount on the subgraph deployment."
  signalAmount: BigInt!
  "Price per share of the subgraph deployment."
  pricePerShare: BigDecimal!
  "List of curator signals derived from the subgraph deployment."
  curatorSignals: [Signal!]! @derivedFrom(field: "subgraphDeployment")
  "Reserve ratio of the subgraph deployment."
  reserveRatio: Int!
  "Manifest associated with the subgraph deployment."
  manifest: SubgraphDeploymentManifest
  "Count of subgraphs associated with the deployment."
  subgraphCount: Int!
  "Count of active subgraphs associated with the deployment."
  activeSubgraphCount: Int!
  "Count of deprecated subgraphs associated with the deployment."
  deprecatedSubgraphCount: Int!
  "Indicates if the subgraph deployment has been transferred to Layer 2."
  transferredToL2: Boolean!
  "Timestamp when the subgraph deployment was transferred to Layer 2."
  transferredToL2At: BigInt
  "Block number when the subgraph deployment was transferred to Layer 2."
  transferredToL2AtBlockNumber: BigInt
  "Transaction ID when the subgraph deployment was transferred to Layer 2."
  transferredToL2AtTx: String
  "Total signalled tokens sent to Layer 2."
  signalledTokensSentToL2: BigInt!
  "Total signalled tokens received on Layer 2."
  signalledTokensReceivedOnL2: BigInt!
}"}
